<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="zh-Hant">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>Kuncn | Resume</title>

<style>
body {
  font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI", Roboto;
  margin: 0;
  background: #f5f5f5;
  color: #222;
}

.container {
  max-width: 800px;
  margin: 40px auto;
  background: white;
  padding: 40px;
  border-radius: 12px;
}

h1 { margin-bottom: 5px; }
h2 { margin-top: 30px; border-bottom: 1px solid #eee; }

.skills span {
  display: inline-block;
  background: #eee;
  padding: 6px 10px;
  margin: 5px;
  border-radius: 6px;
}

a { color: #0077cc; text-decoration: none; }
</style>
</head>

<body>
<div class="container">

<h1>Kuncn</h1>
<p>Web Developer | 前端工程師</p>

<h2>關於我</h2>
<p>我是一名對網站開發有熱情的工程師，擅長 HTML、CSS、JavaScript。</p>

<h2>技能</h2>
<div class="skills">
  <span>HTML</span>
  <span>CSS</span>
  <span>JavaScript</span>
  <span>GitHub</span>
</div>

<h2>專案</h2>
<p>
👉 <a href="https://kuncn.uk">我的網站</a>
</p>

<h2>聯絡</h2>
<p>Email: your@email.com</p>

</div>
</body>
</html>
